Package chessai.chessai.lib

Class BitMap

java.lang.Object
chessai.chessai.lib.BitMap
public class BitMap extends Object
Encapsulates a long that stores a 64 bit bitmap. bit 0 (lsb) : A8 ... bit 63 (msb) : H1
